candidates.title: Introduce merge config feature
candidates.body:
Existing config YAML only assign one config into one path,
not supporting structured setup.
We can support merge for config so that common config can be shared between several paths.

candidates.title: Implement experimental format command.
candidates.body:
This can't parse many syntax supported by Ledger,
so it's still experimetnal.

candidates.title: Support Windows by path / CRLF.
candidates.body: Some tests were failing because of compatibility issue.

candidates.title: Account width larger than expected / double-byte characters
candidates.body:
* Cumulative minor fix related to cargo clippy warnings.
* Insert account / amount spacing (double spaces) even when the account is so long.
* Calculate the account column using unicode-width crate to support CJK characters.

candidates.title: Add multi currency support in CSV
candidates.body:
While ISO Camt053 has a currency support, CSV doesn't.
Implemented the currency support.

candidates.title: Change CLI invocation, documented README.md.
candidates.body: We need to finalize CLI before sharing to the Qiita.

candidates.title: Csv common platform
candidates.body: Use common extract platform for CSV as well.

candidates.title: Support Charges not included in ISO Camt053.
candidates.body: Support Charges which was originally excluded from the amount.

candidates.title: Support charge
candidates.body:
It'll add Chrgs (charge) support for ISO Camt import.
Also it'll add integration test.

candidates.title: Iso camt prerequistes
candidates.body: Introduce some prerequisite changes needed for ISO Camt053 format.

candidates.title: Add index-based CSV config
candidates.body: It doesn't have implementation, just config only.
